      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 94: The Android 11 package visibility fix only declares image/video capture intents. Audio message recording usually resolves an ACTION_RECORD_SOUND / MediaStore audio capture intent, so audio recording apps can still be invisible on Android 11+, leaving the reported audio-message path unfixed. Add the audio capture query as well, using the same action used by ConversationFragment.\\n```suggestion\\n    \u003cqueries\u003e\\n        \u003cintent\u003e\\n            \u003caction android:name\u003d\\\"android.media.action.VIDEO_CAPTURE\\\" /\u003e\\n        \u003c/intent\u003e\\n        \u003cintent\u003e\\n            \u003caction android:name\u003d\\\"android.media.action.IMAGE_CAPTURE\\\" /\u003e\\n        \u003c/intent\u003e\\n        \u003cintent\u003e\\n            \u003caction android:name\u003d\\\"android.provider.MediaStore.RECORD_SOUND\\\" /\u003e\\n        \u003c/intent\u003e\\n    \u003c/queries\u003e\\n```",
      "revId": "9ab01322ec20e9f0a65a4c9b2fe8c2c4520b46a0",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
